(692, 407, 'hotel_common_info', 'a:1:{i:1;a:1:{i:1;s:968:"<p><b>\r\nKHAOSAN SAPPORO FAMILY HOSTEL</b><br>\r\n<p>\r\nAddress: 8-2-17 Minami-Sanjo-Nishi, Chuo, Sapporo, Hokkaido <a href=https://www.google.com/maps?ll=43.055962,141.346485&z=16&t=m&hl=ja&gl=JP&mapclient=embed&cid=16706560360721665077 target="blank">Google Map</a><br>\r\n<p>\r\nPhone: +81-11-233-0036<br>\r\n<p>\r\nE-mail: \r\n<a href="mailto:sapporo@khaosan-tokyo.com">sapporo@khaosan-tokyo.com</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n*Online reservation only<br>\r\n*Reception business hour\r\n8am - 9pm<br>\r\n*Check-in: 3pm - 1am<br>\r\n*Check-out: by 11am<br>\r\n*No curfew<br>\r\n*Free Luggage Keeping: 8am (on the day of check in) – 8pm (on the day of check out)<br>\r\n*Ski and snowboarding gears can be kept in a storage during your stay<br>\r\n*Arrangements can be made for early check-out (before 8:00am) and late check-in (after 21:00pm or before 15:00pm). Informing us in advance is preferable.<br>\r\n*We adhere to the check-in time since we would like to secure our cleaning time: 11:00 – 15:00.\r\n</p>";}}'),
