(1617, 812, 'hotel_common_info', 'a:1:{i:1;a:1:{i:1;s:895:"<p><b>\r\nKHAOSAN ATAMI ONSEN RYOKAN & HOSTEL</b><br>\r\n<p>\r\nAddress: 9-8 Kaiko-Cho, Atami City, Shizuoka <a href=https://www.google.co.jp/maps/place/35%C2%B006''29.0%22N+139%C2%B005''01.1%22E/@35.1075728,139.0838424,19z/data=!4m2!3m1!1s0x0:0x0 target="blank">Google Map</a><br>\r\n<p>\r\nPhone: +81-557-81-6780<br>\r\n<p>\r\nE-mail: \r\n<a href="mailto:atami@khaosan-tokyo.com">atami@khaosan-tokyo.com</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n*Online reservation only<br>\r\n*Reception business hour\r\n8am - 9pm<br>\r\n*Check-in: 3pm - 9pm<br>\r\n*Check-out: by 11am<br>\r\n*No curfew<br>\r\n*Free Luggage Keeping: 8am (on the day of check in) – 8pm (on the day of check out)<br>\r\n*Arrangements can be made for early check-out (before 8:00am) and late check-in (after 21:00pm or before 15:00pm). Informing us in advance is preferable.<br>\r\n*We adhere to the check-in time since we would like to secure our cleaning time: 11:00 – 15:00.\r\n</p>";}}'),
