(407, 1, '2015-12-07 14:39:15', '2015-12-07 05:39:15', '<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">Welcome to KHAOSAN SAPPORO FAMILY HOSTEL!!!</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/GroupLiving.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/GroupLiving-300x199.jpg" alt="GroupLiving" width="300" height="199" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1422" align="left" hspace="20" /></a>Welcome to Khasoan Sapporo Family Hostel! We opened in 2013 as the first branch of Khaosan Hostel chain in Hokkaido. \r\nWe offer accommodation for families and backpackers alike. Many travelers from across the globe stay with us on a regular basis: These include visitors from Europe, Malaysia, Taiwan, Thailand, USA, Australia, China and South Korea. \r\nWe provide dormitory rooms for backpackers and spacious en-suite rooms for families or group travelers including children.\r\nThe facilities of our hostel include a cosy living room, a large common kitchen, a table tennis room and a luggage storage room. Our location is very convenient as we have easy access to Susukino subway station by foot. Many restaurants, shops and sightseeing spots are in proximity of our hostel. \r\nIn winter, you can experience Hokkaido''s unique powder snow and go skiing in one of the many ski resorts close by while in summer, you can enjoy the great nature of Hokkaido and join one of the many festivals.\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">Q&A</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/?p=1344" target="_blank">"Click Here"</a> for details.\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\r\n', 'KHAOSAN SAPPORO FAMILY HOSTEL', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'international-hostel-khaosan-sapporo', '', '', '2016-01-18 17:48:19', '2016-01-18 08:48:19', '',