(507, 1, '2016-01-14 14:32:30', '2016-01-14 05:32:30', '<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">Welcome to KHAOSAN TOKYO KABUKI!!!</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\nGreat location, Friendly staff, Best place to meet new people!! \n\nWhat’s around Kabuki ?\nLocated in the main part in Asakusa.\nOnly 1min walking from Asakusa Station.\nKaminarimon-gate & Sensoji-temple\n(The most famous spot in Asakusa) is just around the corner.\nEverything is around us!\nSupermarket, Drug store, Bunk, Restaurant, Tourist information center\nAlso,30min walking to \nthe Skytree tower(tallest tower in japan)\nSumo stadium Ueno area(Park, Zoo, Market, Museums)\nGet around by Train/Subway! *No need to transfer *\nFrom Narita airport:About 1hour \nFrom Haneda airport:About 45min\nTo Shibuya:About 35min\nTo Ginza :About 15min\nTo Akihabara:10min\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\n\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">Q&A</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/?p=1334" target="_blank">"Click Here"</a> for details.\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->', 'KHAOSAN TOKYO KABUKI', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '246-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-01-14 14:32:30', '2016-01-14 05:32:30', '', 246, 'http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/246-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
