(554, 1, '2016-01-15 17:40:31', '2016-01-15 08:40:31', '<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">Google Map</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=zLqLT65JvsG4.k0hhz4CxeRJM" width="100%" height="400"></iframe>\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">\nACCESS FROM ASAKUSA STATION\n</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/アクセスMAPオリジナル2012英語1.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/アクセスMAPオリジナル2012英語1-300x300.jpg" alt="アクセスMAPオリジナル2012英語" width="300" height="300" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-556" /></a>\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\n\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">\nFrom Toei Asakusa line Asakusa station\n</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/改札.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/改札-300x225.jpg" alt="改札" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-553" /></a>\n1. This is the gate of Asakusa station. Please go left to the stairs or straight to the lift.\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/行き方2.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/行き方2-300x225.jpg" alt="行き方2" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-555" /></a>\n2. When you get the road, you will see Family Mart convenience store in front. Then go right.\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/行き方3.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/行き方3-300x225.jpg" alt="行き方3" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-557" /></a>\n3. Cross the road and turn right.\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/行き方4.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/行き方4-300x225.jpg" alt="行き方4" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-558" /></a>\n4. Turn left. Don''t cross the bridge.\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_2539.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_2539-300x225.jpg" alt="IMG_2539" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-559" /></a>\n5. Then you will see us:D\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\n\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">\nFrom Ginza line Asakusa station\n</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/DSCN0747.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/DSCN0747-300x225.jpg" alt="DSCN0747" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-560" /></a>\n1. This is Ginza line Asakusa station.\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/DSCN0748.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/DSCN0748-300x225.jpg" alt="DSCN0748" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-561" /></a>\n2. Go to exit 4.\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/右へ.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/右へ-300x225.jpg" alt="右へ" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-563" /></a>\n3. Turn right.\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/DSCN0751.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/DSCN0751-300x225.jpg" alt="DSCN0751" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-562" /></a>\n4. Just go straight.\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/DSCN0752.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/DSCN0752-300x225.jpg" alt="DSCN0752" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-564" /></a>\n5. Then you will find us:D\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\n\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">\nACCESS FROM AIRPORT\n</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/transportmap1.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/transportmap1-300x210.jpg" alt="transportmap" width="300" height="210" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-565" /></a>\n\nFrom Narita Airport （about75min/1,060yen）\n(Keisei Line Limited-Express or Express/Unreserved seat)　⇒　Asakusa　Sta.\nIf it is the train gose to UENO, Change for ASAKUSA at AOTO station. It''s very easy! \nSame platform and just opposite side.\n\nFrom Narita Airport \n（Keisei Skyiner/61mini/1,920yen/reserved seat）\n>> Keisei Ueno Sta.(about 3 min walk)　\n>> Ueno Sta.（Ginza Subway Line /5min/160yen） \n>> Asakusa Sta.\n\nFrom Haneda Airport \n（Keikyu Airport Line/45min/640yen）　\n>> Asakusa Sta.\n\nFrom Narita Airport JAPAN RAIL PASS.\n（Narita Express/60min/2,940yen/reserved seat）\n>> JR Tokyo sta.（JR Yamanote Line or JR Keihintouhoku Line/7min/150yen）\n>> Ueno sta.（Ginza Subway Line /5min/160yen） \n>> Asakusa Sta.\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '318-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-01-15 17:40:31', '2016-01-15 08:40:31', '', 318, 'http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/318-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
