(580, 1, '2016-01-15 17:35:17', '2016-01-15 08:35:17', '<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">Google Map</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=zLqLT65JvsG4.kxeN0K3IumTI" width="640" height="480"></iframe>\n</div>\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">\nAccess Map from Station\n</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Lab_map2.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Lab_map2-300x204.jpg" alt="Lab_map2" width="300" height="204" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-579" /></a>\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\n\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">\nFrom Metro Ginza Line Tawaramachi Station\n</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n1. Please take exit No.3 from Tawaramachi Station and continue straight for approximately 2 minutes.\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lab_access1.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lab_access1-300x226.jpg" alt="lab_access1" width="300" height="226" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-581" /></a>\n\n2. Turn left at he 3rd corner, where you will find a Police box.\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lab_access2.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lab_access2-300x226.jpg" alt="lab_access2" width="300" height="226" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-582" /></a>\n\n3. You will see a Khaosan Tokyo laboratory on your right-hand side.\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lab_access3.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lab_access3-300x219.jpg" alt="lab_access3" width="300" height="219" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-583" /></a>\n\nWelcome!!(^-^) / \n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lab_access4.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/lab_access4-300x225.jpg" alt="lab_access4" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-584" /></a>\n\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\n\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">\nFrom Asakusa station (Toei Asakusa Line)  \n</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n1. Please take exit ''A2b'' from Asakusa Station via elevator.\n2. Cross at the cross walk towards the ''Family Mart'' store directly opposite.\n3. Turn right and go straight towards ''Kaminarimon'' (large red gate with big Japanese lantern).\n4. Turn left at the 4th corner (in front of Kaminarimon), and then follow straight for approximately 3 minutes.\n5. Cross at the cross walk towards the ''Family Mart'' store, then past a Police box on the right side.\n6. You will see Khaosan Tokyo Laboratory on your right-hand side.\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\n\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">\nFrom Airport\n</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/transportmap2.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/transportmap2-300x210.jpg" alt="transportmap" width="300" height="210" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-585" /></a>\nFrom Narita Airport\n（Keisei Skyiner / 45min / 2,470yen / Reserved seat）\n>> Keisei Ueno Sta.\n(about 3 min walk)\n>> Ueno Sta.\n（Metro Ginza Line / 4min / 170yen）\n>> Tawaramachi Sta.\nFrom Narita Airport\n(Keisei Line Limited-Express or Express / 80min / 1,090yen / Unreserved seat)\n>> Asakusa Sta.\n*If the train is bound for Ueno, please change to one for Asakusa at Aoto station.\nYou can take it at the opposite side of the same platform.\nFrom Narita Airport with JAPAN RAIL PASS.\n（Narita Express / 60min / 2,940yen / Reserved seat）\n>> JR Tokyo Sta.\n（JR Yamanote/Keihin-touhoku Line / 7min / 150yen）\n>> Ueno Sta.\n（Metro Ginza Line / 4min / 160yen）\n>> Tawaramachi Sta.\nFrom Haneda Airport\n（Keikyu Airport Line / 45min / 650yen）\n>> Asakusa Sta.\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\n\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">\nEasy Access To...\n</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\nTo Ueno (4 min by subway / 10 min by bicycle)\nTo Akihabara (5 min by Tsukuba Express / 20 min by bicycle)\nTo Tsukiji fish market (15 min by subway)\nTo the Imperial Palace (20 min by train/subway)\nTo Shibuya / Harajuku / Shinjuku / Roppongi (30 min by train/subway)\nTo Narita Airport (80 min by Keisei Line)\nTo Haneda Airport (45 min by Keikyu Line)\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '327-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-01-15 17:35:17', '2016-01-15 08:35:17', '', 327, 'http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/327-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
