(599, 1, '2015-12-11 17:31:25', '2015-12-11 08:31:25', '<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">Google Map</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\n<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/u/0/embed?mid=zLqLT65JvsG4.kLpvNg2LpLC0" width="100%" height="400"></iframe>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\r\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">\r\nAccess from JR Kanazawa station\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\n1. Please exit from JR Kanazawa Port Gate exit (West exit)\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本1-thumb-500x311-11145.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本1-thumb-500x311-11145-300x187.jpg" alt="原本1-thumb-500x311-11145" width="300" height="187" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-608" /></a>\r\n\r\n2. After getting outside, please turn left and keep straight until you find an elevator.\r\nPlease take this elevator to underground passage.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本2-thumb-500x591-11146.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本2-thumb-500x591-11146-253x300.jpg" alt="原本2-thumb-500x591-11146" width="253" height="300" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-607" /></a>\r\n\r\n3. Turn left and keep straight until the end of underground passage.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本3-thumb-500x275-11147.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本3-thumb-500x275-11147-300x165.jpg" alt="原本3-thumb-500x275-11147" width="300" height="165" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-606" /></a>\r\n\r\n4. Keep straight until you find second traffic signal. \r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本4-thumb-500x375-11148.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本4-thumb-500x375-11148-300x225.jpg" alt="原本4-thumb-500x375-11148" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-605" /></a>\r\n\r\n5. You should find ''Family Mart'' on your left side. Please turn left at this Family Mart.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本5-thumb-500x375-11149.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本5-thumb-500x375-11149-300x225.jpg" alt="原本5-thumb-500x375-11149" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-604" /></a>\r\n\r\n\r\n6. Soon you will find a fire station. Please turn left.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本6-thumb-500x246-11153.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本6-thumb-500x246-11153-300x148.jpg" alt="原本6-thumb-500x246-11153" width="300" height="148" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-603" /></a>\r\n\r\n7. You should find a narrow street on your right side. Please turn right and you can see our hostel.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本7-thumb-500x375-11157.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/原本7-thumb-500x375-11157-300x225.jpg" alt="原本7-thumb-500x375-11157" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-602" /></a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '599-2', '', '', '2016-01-15 17:59:03', '2016-01-15 08:59:03', '', 365, 'http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/?post_type=access&#038;p=599', 0, 'access', '', 0),
