(640, 1, '2015-12-11 20:07:46', '2015-12-11 11:07:46', '<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">\nAccess Map from Station\n</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/アクセス河原町　英語.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/アクセス河原町　英語-300x205.jpg" alt="アクセス河原町　英語" width="300" height="205" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-635" /></a>\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\n\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">\nFrom Hankyu Kawaramachi Station\n</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n1. When you get out of Exit 10, you will see an arcade called Teramachi right in front of you. Go across the street and go straight through the arcade.\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/kawaramachi1.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/kawaramachi1-300x219.jpg" alt="kawaramachi1" width="300" height="219" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-639" /></a>\n\n2. After five minute walk, you will find a mailbox. It is Rokkaku-dori (Rokkaku St.). Turn left here.\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/kawaramachi3.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/kawaramachi3-300x225.jpg" alt="kawaramachi3" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-638" /></a>\n\n3. Right after the mail box, you will find 7 Eleven at the corner. Turn left here. Then it is our street !\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/kawaramachi4.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/kawaramachi4-300x225.jpg" alt="kawaramachi4" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-637" /></a>\n\n4. 30 meters down the street you will find Khaosan Kyoto Theater on the right side. (There is a parking space and a Japanese restaurant on the other side of the street)\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/kawaramachi5.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/kawaramachi5-300x225.jpg" alt="kawaramachi5" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-636" /></a>\n\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\n\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\n<div class="detail_tittle">\nFrom Shijo Kawaramachi Bus Stop\n</div>\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\n\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\n<div class="detail_text">\n1. When you get off the bus, go to the same direction as the bus you just got off.\n2. Turn left at the first corner, it is Takoyakushi-dori (Takoyakushi Street)\n3. You will find a big green sign of "SHIN KYOGOKU" at the end of the street. Turn right here.\n4. Right after turning right at the green sign, first left. You will see the sign of "TERAMACHI" above you. Go straight through the arcade.\n5. After going through the arcade, first right (you will find a lot of cigarette vending machine). This is our street !\n6. After 20 meters you will find Khaosan Kyoto on the left side of the street! (on the other side of vending machines)\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/B8.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/B8-300x225.jpg" alt="B8" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-644" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/B6.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/B6-300x228.jpg" alt="B6" width="300" height="228" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-645" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/B4.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/B4-300x228.jpg" alt="B4" width="300" height="228" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-646" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/B3.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/B3-300x228.jpg" alt="B3" width="300" height="228" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-647" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/B2.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/B2-300x225.jpg" alt="B2" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-648" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/B1.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/B1-300x225.jpg" alt="B1" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-649" /></a>\n</div>\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->', '', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '634-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-12-11 20:07:46', '2015-12-11 11:07:46', '', 634, 'http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/634-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
