(650, 1, '2015-12-11 20:14:46', '2015-12-11 11:14:46', '<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">\r\nFrom station to the hostel\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/kyotomap_en.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/kyotomap_en-300x180.jpg" alt="kyotomap_en" width="300" height="180" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-651" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">\r\nThe way to the hostel from Kawaramachi station\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\n\r\n1. Go up the stairs at Exit 10\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/ten.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/ten-300x225.jpg" alt="ten" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-653" /></a>\r\n\r\n2. Take right on the street you will see on the right side. You will see a convenience store called Family Mart on the right side. Our hostel isjust 30meters down the street from this convenience store, on the right side of the street.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/shijofuji.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/shijofuji-300x225.jpg" alt="shijofuji" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-652" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">\r\nThe way to the hostel from Shijo station\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\n1. Go out North ticket gate and go straight\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/shijosta.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/shijosta-300x225.jpg" alt="shijosta" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-660" /></a>\r\n\r\n\r\n2. Go up the stairs and turn right\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/step-300x225.jpg" alt="step" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-659" /></a>\r\n\r\n3. Walk straight about 15 minutes or take Hankyu Train \r\n(2 mins to Kawaramachi sta by HankyuTrain / 150 JPY)\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/uw.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/uw-300x225.jpg" alt="uw" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-658" /></a>\r\n\r\n4. Walk straight  until you see Exit 10 if you walk underground\r\n＊Please refer to The way to the hostel fom Kawaramachi station. \r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/ug.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/ug-300x225.jpg" alt="ug" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-657" /></a>\r\n\r\n5. Take an escalator at Exit 19 and turn right and walk straight 15 minutes\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/st.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/st-300x225.jpg" alt="st" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-656" /></a>\r\n\r\n6.  You will see Fujii Daimaru department store on the right side. Take right on the street.  You will see a convenience store called Family Mart on the right side. Our hostel is just 30meters down the street from this convenience store, on the right side of the street.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/fujishijo.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/fujishijo-300x225.jpg" alt="fujishijo" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-655" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">\r\nThe way to the hostel by city bus\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\n1. Take a city bus from Kyoto station to "Shijo Kawaramachi" bus stop by bus #205, #4,  #17, #5\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/opa.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/opa-300x147.jpg" alt="opa" width="300" height="147" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-661" /></a>\r\n\r\n2. The closest bus stop to our hostel is Shijo-Kawaramachi. It''s located in front of the OPA department store. After leaving the bus at Shijo-Kawaramachi, face to your left and walk straight to go across the street.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/takashimaya.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/takashimaya-300x225.jpg" alt="takashimaya" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-662" /></a>\r\n\r\n3. You will see Takashimaya Department Store in front of you. After crossing the street, walk right and then keep walking for 5 minutes.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/fujii.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/fujii-300x225.jpg" alt="fujii" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-663" /></a>\r\n\r\n4. Turn left at the Teramachi dori street next to Fujii Daimaru Department Store. You will see a convenience store called Family Mart on the right side. Our hostel is just 30 meters down the street from this convenience store, on the right side of the street.\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '650-2', '', '', '2015-12-11 20:26:07', '2015-12-11 11:26:07', '', 406, 'http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/?post_type=access&#038;p=650', 0, 'access', '', 0),
