(664, 1, '2015-12-11 20:37:49', '2015-12-11 11:37:49', '<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">Google Map</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\n<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2915.3393070328716!2d141.34426371561065!3d43.05533079890172!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x5f0b298ff34098c7%3A0xe7d9a022076fcc35!2zSW50ZXJuYXRpb25hbCBIb3N0ZWwgS2hhb3NhbiBTYXBwb3JvKOOCpOODs-OCv-ODvOODiuOCt-ODp-ODiuODq-ODm-OCueODhuODqyDjgqvjgqrjgrXjg7PmnK3luYwp!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sjp!4v1450673248722" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">\r\nHow to get to Khaosan Sapporo\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/7d077fa52e8cc8937eb432f57e08e280.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/7d077fa52e8cc8937eb432f57e08e280-300x191.jpg" alt="7d077fa52e8cc8937eb432f57e08e280" width="300" height="191" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-665" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">\r\nHow to get to Khaosan Sapporo from Susukino subway station\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\n1. From JR Sapporo station, please take “Nanboku subway line” to go to Susukino subway station.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access1.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access1-300x225.jpg" alt="Access1" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-666" /></a>\r\n\r\n2. At Susukino subway station, please head for “Exit 2”.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access2.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access2-300x225.jpg" alt="Access2" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-667" /></a>\r\n\r\n3. After going up to the ground, please walk straightly along the pathway.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access3.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access3-300x225.jpg" alt="Access3" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-668" /></a>\r\n\r\n4. This is the first traffic light. You can see a convenience store. Please keep going.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access4.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access4-300x225.jpg" alt="Access4" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-669" /></a>\r\n\r\n5. This is the second traffic light. Please keep going.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access5.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access5-300x225.jpg" alt="Access5" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-670" /></a>\r\n\r\n6. This is the third traffic light. You can see “Shiseikan Elementary school”.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access6.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access6-300x225.jpg" alt="Access6" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-671" /></a>\r\n\r\n7. This is the fourth traffic light. Please turn right at the corner.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access7.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access7-300x225.jpg" alt="Access7" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-672" /></a>\r\n\r\n8. Just after the corner, you can see cleaners as this picture shows.\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access8.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access8-300x225.jpg" alt="Access8" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-673" /></a>\r\n\r\n9. Next to the cleaners, there is a brown 6 floors building. Welcome to Khaosan Sapporo!!!\r\n<a href="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access9.jpg"><img src="http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/Access9-300x225.jpg" alt="Access9" width="300" height="225" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-674" /></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">\r\nAccess\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\n●From CityTram「Shiseikan shogakko mae stop」 1min by walk\r\n●From Jotetsu bus「Shiseikan shogakko mae stop」1min by walk\r\n●From Subway Nanboku line「Susukino Sta.」Tozai line「Nishi11chome」7min by walk\r\n●From JR「Sapporo Sta.」 min by car\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->\r\n\r\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">\r\nFrom airports to Sapporo JR station\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\n●From New Chitose airport to JR Sapporo Sta. by 「Rapid Airport Express」　1,070yen／36min\r\n●From New Chitose airport to Tokyo dorm hotel sapporo by 「Airporst bus」　1,030円／80min timetable\r\n●Okadama Airport to Sapporo Sta. by 「Hokuto kotsu Airporst bus」 　400yen／30min\r\n●Okadama Airport to Sapporo terminal by Sapporo chuo bus 　210yen／35min\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->', '', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '664-2', '', '', '2015-12-24 10:47:32', '2015-12-24 01:47:32', '', 407, 'http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/?post_type=access&#038;p=664', 0, 'access', '', 0),
