(1344, 1, '2016-01-12 15:48:50', '2016-01-12 06:48:50', '<!-- この処理がある場合、タイトルが非表示となります -->\r\n<style>.tittle_text {display: none;}</style>\r\n<!-- タイトルここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_tittle">Questions about Khaosan Sapporo Family Hostel</div>\r\n<!-- タイトルここまで -->\r\n<!-- コンテンツここから -->\r\n<div class="detail_text">\r\nIs there a curfew?\r\n・There is no curfew in our hostel. Please be considerate for other guests during the night time.\r\n\r\nHow can I book?\r\n・Please book from our website.\r\n・Credit card is needed when you book online.\r\n\r\nDo you provide amenities such as shampoo, soap, and etc?\r\n・We provide some amenities such as rinse-in-shampoo, body soap, cotton buds and hand-soap. Bath towel and toothbrush are available for an extra charge of 50YEN.\r\n\r\nIs there any convenience store near the hostel?\r\n・There are convenience stores, supermarkets, pharmacies, and a 100YEN shop within 5～10mins walk from our hostel\r\n\r\nIs there internet available in your hostel? How about WI-FI?\r\n・Free WI-FI access is available in our hostel.\r\n・There are 6 computers in the living room. (Free of charge, 24hours)\r\n\r\nIs there any bicycle rental service available?\r\n・In Summer, we have rental bicycles available free of charge. (Based on availability/deposit required)\r\n\r\nAre bed linen include in the room fee?\r\n・Room fees include linens such as pillow case, bed sheets, and blankets.\r\n\r\nWhere are our guests from?\r\n・Our guests are from many countries such as Japan, Taiwan, China, South Korea, Thailand, Hong Kong,\r\nSingapore, Malaysia, Australia, United States,  Europe and etc.\r\n\r\nCan I pay by credit card on check in?\r\n・Yes, we can accept credit card (Visa, Master, AMEX, JCB, Unionpay) but there is a surcharge of 5%\r\n\r\nCan I stay with my children in a dorm room?\r\n・We are afraid that we cannot accommodate children under the age of 10 in any dormitory room. Please book a private room to stay with children.\r\n・All children under 4 years stay at no extra charge when using existing beds.\r\n・All children aged 4 or over stay at adult rate even when using existing beds.\r\n\r\nIs there a security locker in the dormitory room?\r\n・Yes, we provide a security locker for valuables for each guests in our dormitory rooms.\r\n\r\nIs there any bank? Where do I exchange or withdraw money?\r\n・Banks are situated near Odori station. (ATM/Exchange)\r\n・Post office is 2 blocks away from our hostel and just 5min walk. (ATM/Exchange)\r\n・Seven Eleven (24 hours ATM available)\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- コンテンツここまで -->', 'sapporo Q&A', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sapporo-qa', '', '', '2016-01-14 12:46:15', '2016-01-14 03:46:15', '', 1118, 'http://khaosan-test.sakura.ne.jp/?page_id=1344', 0, 'page', '', 0),
